track.name: I'd Do Anything To Make You Smile

wiki.summary: Similar to Kanye’s use of romantic metaphor in MBDTF, Jack Harlow articulates the rap game as a romantic partner who he is able to do anything he wants to, which is the central concept of the Come Home The Kids Miss You. This is not completely unexpected as Jack is a big fan of Kanye’s work and recently collaborated with the rap legend. During the week ending May 21, 2022, “I’d Do Anything To Make You Smile” peaked at #88 on the Hot 100. Read more on Last.fm.
